      "description": "<p><a name=\"_Hlk197877002\">Corpo a corpo, Invocação</a></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\">A partir de seus braços lança um enxame se insetos que segue um caminho estipulado perturbando a todos.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Esforço:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 5.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Tempo de preparo:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 2 ações.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Alcance:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> trajeto de 15m.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Dano:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> [ESP] Biológico: Tóxico.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Efeitos:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> Indireto, aplica MOD-3 as ações.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Duração:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 1+</span><span style=\"mso-bookmark:_Hlk197877002\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family:'MS Mincho';mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">Ⓐ</span></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> rodadas. </span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.